Case No: 1
     
Check location in the home tab is the same with categories tab
----------------------------------------------------------------

* Open the Hepsiburada
* Go to the location section on home tab
* Set the location
* Check the 'Location is saved.' pop-up
* Go to the Categories Tab
* Select any category and go to the list page
* Check the city at the 'Yarin Kapinda' section is the same with saved city
